      "title": "Sri Lanka won the second Test against Pakistan",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lanka: 378/10 (Battle: Dinesh Chandimal 80, Niroshan Dickwella 51, Oshada Fernando 50, Angelo Mathews 42, Dimuth Karunaratne 40, Ramesh Mendis 35, Dhananjaya de Silva 33 runs. Bowling: Naseem Shah 3/58, Yasir Shah 3/ 83, Mohammad Nawaz 2/80, Nelaman Ali 1/64)",
        "Pakistan: 231/10 (Battling: Agha Salman 62, Imam-ul-Haq 32, Yasir Shah 26, Hasan Ali 21 runs. Bowling: Ramesh Mendis 5/47, Prabhat Jayasuriya 3/80 Dhananjaya de Silva 1/15, Asita Fernando 1/62)",
        "Sri Lanka: 360/8 (Battling: Dhananjaya de Silva 109, Dimuth Karunaratne 61, Ramesh Mendes AA 45, Angelo Mathews 35 runs. Bowling: Naseem Shah 2/44, Mohammad Nawaz 2/75, Akha Salman 1/41, Nelaman Ali 1/54, Yasir Shah 1/80)",
